{"tid":920591,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣次次塞車cut完線會打兩下死火燈","createTime":"2018-11-29T02:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:30:18.000Z","uid":14958,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"83296eb80fb6f149d8f15f5f17317929c5f54c78","tid":920591,"uid":14958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"已成習慣<br />\n<br />\n但又成日驚後車以為我玩野 cut完佢扮死火<br />\n<br />\n可能得巴士司機明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f5efa27da2a47e60fd3e72ba505dec777e3010","tid":920591,"uid":209021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187c0fb52f1e6cda3587cd96053e2d5358970af9","tid":920591,"uid":152141,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"我會打<br />\n但我都一樣驚後面以為我玩野"},{"pid":"625008fb8488a2e0d4256ab590eeecac32751a89","tid":920591,"uid":66242,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日喺東隧 cut 線<br />\n諗住拉錬入<br />\n點知左面應該到佢嗰架車又唔跟上嚟<br />\n以為佢讓啦<br />\n咁我打燈咪入囉<br />\n仲遞埋手比五<br />\n後尾睇番倒後鏡個阿伯隔咗幾架車都仲未入到隊<br />\n可能佢外國回流番香港無耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fd6387c30841eb511038ab2723810ad38ecdde","tid":920591,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"83296eb80fb6f149d8f15f5f17317929c5f54c78","tid":920591,"uid":14958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"已成習慣<br />\n<br />\n但又成日驚後車以為我玩野 cut完佢扮死火<br />\n<br />\n可能得巴士司機明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"細車普通車遞手比五咪算<br />\n因為後後後車睇到會唔知咩事<br />\n巴士因為大架擋住後面<br />\n後後車睇唔到<br />\n所以可以打死火燈專俾佢睇"},{"pid":"002cf5ea1635079ca10762616a3f2063e3ac6def","tid":920591,"uid":110877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:58:10.000Z","msg":"我比五就算"},{"pid":"189d3e7821741fed505db25b0b9f34dee6c0b7df","tid":920591,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"一邊cut一邊較低車窗比個5字<br />\n尤其cutd 連企位企滿哂乘客巴士<br />\n車入面d乘客一定覺得<br />\n呢類司機咁有禮貌香港好罕有<br />\n<br />\n有無人覺得好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3f8435c854de6b91968ed3a9851cc63bfc0768","tid":920591,"uid":139991,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"我會比先五蚊先再打兩下，感覺令後車覺得我唔係玩野，同埋好鐘意讓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好鐘意佢地比五蚊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4ecf50f74e5915f21493f39bdfce3218836d6b","tid":920591,"uid":29423,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"189d3e7821741fed505db25b0b9f34dee6c0b7df","tid":920591,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"一邊cut一邊較低車窗比個5字<br />\n尤其cutd 連企位企滿哂乘客巴士<br />\n車入面d乘客一定覺得<br />\n呢類司機咁有禮貌香港好罕有<br />\n<br />\n有無人覺得好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"Cut人地巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我覺得我一架私家車<br />\n載得一兩個人<br />\n但人地一架滿員巴士有成百人<br />\n人地係高效率好多<br />\n所以平時會主動讓巴士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我先最撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e081894bc2ee0e501b12952cc754a78ce918a482","tid":920591,"uid":106945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"可惜依家好多俾五蚊既司機老奉硬cut 俾五呢....."},{"pid":"c908af5c54a5cab06531211ca0bcf332a32f38f8","tid":920591,"uid":38033,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"我平時行路cut 線都會比個五後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">家陣睇緊精神科</span>"},{"pid":"023b36e419ca8eab440f93713c6815f8c1b100f7","tid":920591,"uid":90267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"英國揸開都係咁<br />\n讓人就閃大燈<br />\n人地讓完你講唔該就閃死火燈<br />\n<br />\n係香港冇呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d16e687c923c43d41a3e9f077b00e129ea7c453","tid":920591,"uid":152141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"023b36e419ca8eab440f93713c6815f8c1b100f7","tid":920591,"uid":90267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"英國揸開都係咁<br />\n讓人就閃大燈<br />\n人地讓完你講唔該就閃死火燈<br />\n<br />\n係香港冇呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"D人成日見我閃大燈以為我唔比佢CUT<br />\n收油閃兩野比佢, 佢放棄唔CUT <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55257407d0a3b42ebe04b8dfd60e6444680619dc","tid":920591,"uid":28522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d16e687c923c43d41a3e9f077b00e129ea7c453","tid":920591,"uid":152141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"023b36e419ca8eab440f93713c6815f8c1b100f7","tid":920591,"uid":90267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"英國揸開都係咁<br />\n讓人就閃大燈<br />\n人地讓完你講唔該就閃死火燈<br />\n<br />\n係香港冇呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:30: